Diffusion Features — Variant A (node-level multi-scale HKS)
Spec: docs/superpowers/specs/2026-05-28-diffusion-features-lp-design.md
Config: trials=50, K=5, datasets=['Cora', 'Chameleon']
========================================================================

Feature: per candidate edge (u,v): concat[HKS(u), HKS(v), |HKS(u)-HKS(v)|]
  = 3K-dim, from normalized-Laplacian heat kernel on the leakage-free
  training graph (val/test pos removed). HKS_t(i)=sum_k exp(-t*lam_k)phi_k(i)^2.

